From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jack Styles <jackrogers.org@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 15 Mar 2026 03:30:00 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Add blocked domains navigation throttle

Integrate StevenBlack/hosts and polarhive/arceo blocklists into Dumb Browser.
Blocks navigation to ~170K domains covering fakenews, gambling, porn, social
media, news, entertainment, and consumerism sites.

The domain list is generated at build time from blocked_domains.txt via a GN
action. A NavigationThrottle intercepts main-frame navigations to blocked
domains and shows a themed error page with plum (#412234) branding.
