+    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 15v-2h2v2h-2zm0-4V7h2v6h-2z"/></svg>
